  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/news/\" rel=\"tag\">科技新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/10/japanese-smart-diaper/\"><img alt=\"Japanese scientist shows off diaper sensor\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/a2481ec4801f789214256f67eaa0ce79/japan-diaper-afp-lead.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n日本人民总是有奇思妙想，上图中这款智能尿布毫无疑问也算是其中之一。其核心是中间那块由东京大学研制成功的曲面感应器（是特意选黄色的吗？），它装有可印制的<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2011/10/21/thinfilm-and-parc-demo-printable-organic-cmos-circuit-inch-us/\">有机电路</a>，能够感应湿度、温度和压力的变化（说气味的那是想多了）。除此之外，它还支持无线充电和传输数据，这样一来照护人员就可以通过手中的接收器，在不脱去外面衣物的情况下查看婴儿或老人是否需要更换尿布了。据悉在搞定功耗问题后这款产品就会上市，不过，穿在身上的东西带电总让人觉得有点慌啊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/10/japanese-smart-diaper/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://japandailypress.com/japan-develops-wireless-sensor-for-diapers-able-to-send-alert-if-needs-changing-1043921/\" target=\"_blank\">Japan Daily Press</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.nst.com.my/latest/japan-sensor-will-let-diaper-say-baby-needs-changing-1.480875\" target=\"_blank\">New Straits Times</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/10/japanese-smart-diaper/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20826715/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/10/japanese-smart-diaper/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
